  "title": "docs(examples): use htm in examples templates",
  "body": "## Summary\r\n\r\nThis updates all examples to use function templates, with `html` when necessary.\r\n\r\nWe're still using string HTML and deprecated APIs when using connectors (e.g., in `example-instantsearch-media`), which we can do another pass on later on as we might be able to use templates and simplify the examples instead of pulling Preact directly.",
